            "body": "> but could do something more or less smart in Python.\r\n\r\nI think what user is going to expect more and more is to be compatible/conforming with typing system of Python. Hence, we should pay attention that pure python cython will be able to be used together with mypy. E.g. it is worth of looking in sqlalchemy how they used pure python: https://github.com/sqlalchemy/sqlalchemy/commit/0be89aaa38d06a9beced7f1bfe2987f4b6afebb8",
            "created_at": "2024-04-07T07:38:32Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/1981#issuecomment-2041352466",
            "id": 2041352466,
